516
00:23:17,333 --> 00:23:19,500
[KYON] Or maybe... getting
involved with this case

517
00:23:19,583 --> 00:23:22,833
was something that
Nagato wished for.

518
00:23:22,916 --> 00:23:25,750
An android made by aliens
living in an empty room

519
00:23:25,833 --> 00:23:27,833
